#define OutputBit ( count   ) 

Value:

{  \

}

#define OutputCode ( code   ) 

Value:

{ \
    accumulator+=code << (32-code_width-number_bits); \
    number_bits+=code_width; \
    while (number_bits >= 8) \
    { \
        (void) WriteBlobByte(image,(unsigned char) (accumulator >> 24)); \
        accumulator=accumulator << 8; \
        number_bits-=8; \
    } \
}
